                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
